{"tid":1365130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"光復香港,時代革命 不只是遊行時既口號","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:13:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:03:14.000Z","uid":47905,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2353316bbe914662d198d1b75a947efced8aaae","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:13:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港,時代革命 係一個理念<br />\n我地要將呢個理念傳開去,唔應該只係遊行個陣叫<br />\n<br />\n呢兩日我搭鐵路個陣都不停諗<br />\n我叫光復香港,會唔會有人應時代革命<br />\n<br />\n我地要將呢個理念傳開去,唔只網上,連儂牆,仲可以係任何位置<br />\n有好多人可能唔上連登,或者無睇連儂牆等等,要令到呢句說明<br />\n記係每個香港人既心<br />\n大家每日搭車返工放工<br />\n都係一個好好既機會,向全車既市民傳達呢個信息<br />\n希望當有人叫光復香港,大家可以叫時代革命<br />\n可以比到更多信心大家,知道背後其實有好多人支持,亦到可以激勵大家既士氣<br />\n當叫完幾次之後<br />\n大家可以講 727 元朗見 728上環見 等等<br />\n將遊行既信息傳開去<br />\n<br />\n口號不應只是遊行時進行<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人跟機一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21703c0816ddc3ea7ee848fe5c5df44b85b02f28","tid":1365130,"uid":134214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"00e3a848d07d57e28acc4d12918b191e27e66af4","tid":1365130,"uid":289262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"將句口號轉做鈴聲有無得諗<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"0e359795013f4199d99a2a5dd043cc637926d4a8","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00e3a848d07d57e28acc4d12918b191e27e66af4","tid":1365130,"uid":289262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"將句口號轉做鈴聲有無得諗<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"都得"},{"pid":"6634c6a33d95a221963e8b9f3bafbcbe639093b5","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"8a7ba0e26a24c0a9c8fc0ddaa968425bac50cfa9","tid":1365130,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:23:45.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fefc53a0de4de1d57e0fc62bd64461cd84881edc","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f587654f7b40ee83c047d7d0af2172630593e80","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf46e013cec9a01362163065ee2015147bab928","tid":1365130,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:08:30.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"8f0ee5bb4b690c6032c776ddc5c1495e9adfe392","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450b50e5a07c0f0ec478690478ed08f0b12675a4","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d2ae25d30f23aadd9e9a08a012bc86d1573590","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a756fc3a58d4bc8b845b54c1b8daf6de234601","tid":1365130,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcacf481ac7c13e39cb0b7853f94206f3c306dc","tid":1365130,"uid":60386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s